data.description: DISCOVER a RARE GEM in this price range! Embrace the charm of small-town living on a spacious 0.44-acre lot. This 1.5-story home boasts 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath, showcasing a generously sized eat-in kitchen with modern countertops, a spacious primary bedroom, and convenient first-floor laundry. Upstairs, a large open bedroom awaits with a cozy sitting area, perfect for relaxation. Storage shed included! Located just a short drive from Fond du Lac, this home offers seamless access to the highway. Don't miss the opportunity to be close to the enchanting Lake Winnebago! Immerse yourself in the warmth and space of this remarkable property. Book a showing now to experience the magic of your potential new home!  AFFORDABLE-AFFORDABLE-AFFORDABLE
